articles.title: No more Taylor Swift! MTV awards canceled over Israel-Hamas conflict - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: Organizers said Thursday this ‘does not feel like a moment for a global celebration.’
articles.content:
Next months MTV Europe Music Awards have been canceled due to the volatility of world events, organizers announced Thursday.
